      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/morgan-stanley-warns-of-forint-slide-on-hungarian-economic-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 警告称，匈牙利福林将大幅下跌，与其他策略师一样，认为匈牙利将面临财政和货币政策风险的双重威胁。]]></description>
